      "line": 49,
      "message": "1. Make logger both static and final, we don't want the reference to be re-assignable :)\n2. rename variable name to lowercase - MsoLogger is not a constant, having the variable reference constant (after adding final) is not enough - the object also needs to be immutable which in this case is not true. For Reference check https://google.github.io/styleguide/javaguide.html#s5.2.4-constant-names",
